Similarly, data science thrives on diverse perspectives and experiences to uncover unique

00:08:26.399 --> 00:08:26.959
insights.

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:33.679
Embracing different viewpoints in both fields can lead to innovation and problem solving.

00:08:35.039 --> 00:08:36.320
So, we get the point, right?

00:08:36.400 --> 00:08:37.599
So, we get the point, right?

