Once you've established that firm foundation and reproducibly cleaning your data, hint,

00:09:31.919 --> 00:09:36.159
hint, okay, organizing it, et cetera, et cetera,

00:09:36.719 --> 00:09:40.080
it's time to choose a tool to manipulate your data.

