But for the sake of time, we're going to focus on type four.

00:11:41.039 --> 00:11:44.080
We'll focus on type four because that's my hair type.

00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:52.479
So, if your hair is type four like my hair, it's tightly coiled with no defined pattern.

00:11:53.119 --> 00:12:01.280
And I equate that to working with super messy data like text data, words, sentences, paragraphs

00:12:01.280 --> 00:12:02.640
of free-flowing text.

00:12:03.440 --> 00:12:04.960
It's unstructured.

00:12:04.960 --> 00:12:07.359
It's not neatly formatted into columns.

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:14.080
And R is a fantastic tool to learn and to use in order to devise patterns from this

00:12:14.080 --> 00:12:17.840
type of data, trends, make predictions, and recommendations.

00:12:18.479 --> 00:12:24.479
You can use it to predict traffic, TikTok algorithms, and even detect unusual bank transactions.

00:12:27.919 --> 00:12:28.799
So, I'll summarize.

00:12:29.760 --> 00:12:34.719
Like Afro-textured hair, there are levels to this thing that we call data science.

00:12:34.719 --> 00:12:40.880
And to break into it successfully, you have to build a strong foundation by learning about

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:47.359
different types of data, what repositories are out there, how do you share and collaborate

00:12:47.359 --> 00:12:50.080
with others, how do you clean it, format it, et cetera.

00:12:50.960 --> 00:12:55.919
Once you have that foundation, so you've taken care of your roots, you have to determine

00:12:55.919 --> 00:12:59.919
the tools that are right for you to get the kind of analysis you want.

00:12:59.919 --> 00:13:01.599
Is it a pressing comb?

00:13:01.599 --> 00:13:02.719
Is it a latch hook?

00:13:03.280 --> 00:13:04.239
Is it braids?

00:13:04.239 --> 00:13:05.840
What are you doing with your data?

00:13:07.119 --> 00:13:12.719
Whether you're using spreadsheets for a numerical operation or you want to jump into the 4B,

00:13:13.440 --> 00:13:18.559
that unstructured data, that not neatly formatted data, and use a tool like R.

00:13:20.159 --> 00:13:24.719
These are a few broad comparisons, but it's important to note that Afro-textured hair

00:13:24.719 --> 00:13:27.520
and data science are distinct and separate domains.

00:13:28.559 --> 00:13:36.159
However, exploring connections between seemingly unrelated topics can often lead to new creative

00:13:36.159 --> 00:13:38.159
